data.description: Welcome home! This adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch on a corner lot has been fully renovated while maintaining original charm. Enjoy morning coffee on the oversized front porch and entertaining friends on the deck overlooking the oversized fenced-in backyard. Inside, you are greeted by an open living area full of natural light and a gourmet kitchen. The owners suite offers a large walk-in closet and stunning ensuite while the secondary bedrooms are spacious and share a bathroom. The details to this home are incredible, from leather marble countertops, built-in speakers in the primary bathroom, 12 foot ceilings, soft close cabinets with built-in rollout drawers, and so much more.  Make this tranquil oasis yours!
